[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]

This is the Queerstyle Theme by [[*user Queerious]], a fork of the existing [[[*theme:blankstyle|BLANKSTYLE]]], by [[*user Placeholder McD]] and [[*user HarryBlank]]. This fork adds some small changes, including modifying the header to be non-Site-43 specific, and replaces font in the headings.

This theme also uses the [[[*component:pride-highlighter|White Outline Classic LGBTQ+ Pride Logo]]] by [[*user Woedenaz]].

The style makes a change to headings specifically within the 'pseudo-div' class, which changes the font-family to Vast Shadow, the font associated with Pseudogenesis Productions. Below is an example of the 'pseudo-div' class, and an example of each heading level.

[[div class="pseudo-div" style="color: white; padding: 0.2em 1em 1em 1em;"]]

+ Heading Level 1
++ Heading Level 2
+++ Heading Level 3
++++ Heading Level 4
+++++ Heading Level 5
++++++ Heading Level 6

[[/div]]

To use Vast Shadow in other places, use the following in your style definitions:
[[div class="code"]]
@@font-family: "Vast Shadow", serif;@@
[[/div]]

To use this theme, please put the following at the top of your page:

[[div class="code"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:blankstyle]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:queerstyle]]@@
[[/div]]

[[div class="blockquote"]]
[[=]]
Important Note! You must include both themes, **in this order**, for the theme to work.
[[/=]]
[[/div]]


This theme is designed for use in Queerious' works, and is available to anyone else that prefers the subtle center alignment of BLANKSTYLE, but for works set outside of Site-43.

[[/iftags]]

[[div [[iftags -theme]]style="display: none"[[/iftags]]]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:toggle-sidebar]]

>[[ift{$fade}gs +theme]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:fade-in speed=3]]
>[[/ift{$fade}gs]]

>[[ift{$acs}gs +theme]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:acs-animation]]
>[[/ift{$acs}gs]]

[[=]]
[[collapsible show="+ CODE" hide="- CODE"]]
[[<]]
[[code type="CSS"]]
/*
    QUEERSTYLE CSS
    By Queerious
    Forked from:
       Blankstyle CSS by Placeholder McD and HarryBlank
    Using:
       White Outline Classic LGBTQ+ Pride Logo by Woedenaz from https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:pride-highlighter
*/
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vast+Shadow&display=swap');

#header h1 a::before {
  font-size: 1.2em;
  text-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #fff;
}

#header h2::before {
  font-size: 0.9em;
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #fff;
}

#header {
    margin-top: 0.5em;
}

:root {
    --header-title: "SCP Foundation";
    --header-subtitle: "SECURE, CONTAIN, PROTECT";
}


@media (max-width: 707px) {
    #header h1 a::before {
        font-size: 9vw;
    }
}

#top-bar, #top-bar a {
  text-shadow: 0.75px 0.75px 1px #fff;
}

div#extra-div-1 {
    height: 150px;
    background-image: url('https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component:pride-highlighter/gp_logo.svg');
}

#page-content .creditButton p a {
    color:#373737;
}

/* Pseudogenesis Formats */

.pseudo-div {
    border:solid 4px #B22A2A;
    background:#403450;
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-family: "Vast Shadow", serif;
    text-align: center;
}

.pseudo-div :is(h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6) {
    font-family: "Vast Shadow", serif;
    letter-spacing: 0px;
    font-weight: normal;
    color: white;
}
[[/code]]
[[/<]]
[[/collapsible]]
[[/=]]
@@ @@

